    "Whether this capability transfers to detecting naturally occurring strong activations (e.g., from emotionally charged prompts) remains an open question.",
    "Lindsey raises the same concern: \"our concept injection protocol places models in an unnatural setting unlike those they face in training or deployment.\"",
    "Mechanistic Uncertainty.",
    "We do not identify the mechanisms underlying trained introspection.",
    "Lindsey speculates on possible minimal mechanisms (anomaly detection circuits, attention heads attending to cached predictions); understanding whether our training induces similar or different mechanisms is important future work.No Evidence for Metacognitive Representation."
